## ðŸ”§ Lab Tasks

### Task 1: Generate Hashes
```bash
cat file1.txt
cat file2.txt
sha256sum file1.txt
sha256sum file2.txt

sha256sum file1.txt >> file1hash
sha256sum file2.txt >> file2hash
cat file1hash
cat file2hash
cmp file1hash file2hash
